class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-3 description-right\">\r\n					<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-126\" <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-128\" src=\"http://localhost:10080/tutorials/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/3.png\"/>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-5 description-right border-left\">\r\n					<label class=\"title\">Individual developers and/or companies</label>\r\n						<p class=\"description description-right\">Are you going to take a new project but you are not sure whether your estimate is correct.\r\n						Or maybe you come up with a huge estimate, but you afraid that your client won’t understand the estimate or will choose a cheaper one, which will definitely fail? \r\n						Then you can ask them again to get third person unbiased estimate.\r\n						</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"row service-row\">\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-5 description-left border-right\">\r\n					<label class=\"title\">You want to partner with an outsourcing company</label>\r\n						<p class=\"description description-left\">Whenever you partner with an outsourcing company to build a product the key to success is a well defined scope of the project. We help you out by writing a world class RFP document - which clearly states the requirements of your project, expected deliverables, acceptance criteria and the handoff. \r\n						</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-3 description-left\">\r\n					<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-129\" src=\"http://localhost:10080/tutorials/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/4.png\"/>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"row service-row\">\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"col-md-3 description-right\">\r\n					<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-130\" src=\"http://localhost:10080/tutorials/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/5.png\"/>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div cl